            <p>- TypeScript</p>
            <p>- APIs: RESTful Web Services</p>
            <p>- Continuous Integration / Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) &amp; DevOps practices</p>
            <p>- Agile / Scrum &amp; TDD / BDD</p>
            <p></p>
            <p>If you meet the above requirements and would be interested in finding out more about this opportunity, please apply with an updated CV ASAP as they are looking to move fairly quickly with these opportunities.</p>
